Package OnlineVoter

Class Election

  • java.lang.Object
    • OnlineVoter.Election
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Election
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Election class contains all the data related to a certain Election. This is:
    1. Start Time
    2. End Time
    3. Title
    4. Description
    5. Departament
    6. Total Vote count
    7. Lists to be voted in
    8. Type of the Election
    9. StartTime
